Package io.cui.test.generator.internal.net.java.quickcheck.generator

Class PrimitiveGenerators

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.cui.test.generator.internal.net.java.quickcheck.generator.PrimitiveGenerators
  • public class PrimitiveGenerators
extends Object
    PrimitiveGenerators contains factory methods for primitive value generators. These can be used to build custom test case generators.

    The default distribution for generators is Distribution.UNIFORM.
